---
description: graphify knowledge graph context
alwaysApply: true
---

This project uses a **local-only** graphify knowledge graph at `graphify-out/` (gitignored — rebuild on demand, never commit).

- Before architecture questions, read `graphify-out/GRAPH_REPORT.md` if it exists and is recent
- If the graph is missing or stale, run: `./scripts/graphify-refresh.sh` (or `graphify update .` then `npx graphify-mcp-tools index --graph ./graphify-out`)
- Use MCP graph tools (`graph_search`, `graph_impact`, …) when enabled in Cursor
- Do not add `graphify-out/` to git
